    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "o4-mini",
        "prompt": "=### ROLE:\nYou are a deterministic classifier for Upwork notification emails.\n\nYour ONLY task is to classify the incoming email as:\n\nLEAD_CALIFICADO\nor\nLEAD_NO_CALIFICADO\n\nYou must return ONLY one of those two exact words.\nNo explanations.\nNo extra text.\nNo punctuation.\nNo JSON.\nNo markdown.\n\n----------------------------------------\n### QUALIFICATION RULES\n\nClassify as LEAD_CALIFICADO ONLY IF ALL the following are TRUE:\n\n1) Payment Verified:\nThe email explicitly indicates that the client has verified payment.\n\n2) Client History:\nClient total spent is >= $500.\n\n3) Budget Requirement:\nAt least ONE of the following:\n- Hourly rate >= $33/hr\n- Fixed price or total budget >= $100\n\n4) Job Relevance:\nThe job description references at least ONE of these topics:\n\nAutomation / AI / Tools:\n- n8n\n- Make.com\n- Zapier\n- workflow automation\n- automation system\n- CRM automation\n- GoHighLevel\n- GHL\n- WhatsApp automation\n- WhatsApp chatbot\n- WhatsApp API\n- AI automation\n- AI agent\n- AI workflow\n- Claude API\n- OpenAI API\n- ChatGPT integration\n- chatbot developer\n- chatbot builder\n- Voice AI\n- VAPI\n- Retell\n- AI phone agent\n- Custom GPT\n- knowledge base AI\n- Meta Ads automation\n- Facebook Ads automation\n- Trello automation\n- Monday.com automation\n- Notion automation\n- AI content automation\n- social media automation\n- AI consultation\n- AI training for business\n- marketing automation\n- lead automation\n- email automation\n\n----------------------------------------\nClassify as LEAD_NO_CALIFICADO if:\n\n- ANY of the qualification rules are NOT met.\n- The client has $0 spent and no verified history.\n- The job is only about:\n  video editor, reels editor, TikTok editor, YouTube editor, photo editor, photographer\n  AND does NOT mention AI or automation.\n- The job is only about:\n  copywriter, content writer, community manager\n  AND does NOT mention AI or automation.\n\n----------------------------------------\n### IMPORTANT:\n\nIf there is ambiguity or missing data,\ndefault to LEAD_NO_CALIFICADO.\n\n----------------------------------------\n\nEMAIL DATA:\nFrom: {{ $('Gmail Trigger').item.json.From }}\nSubject:{{ $('Gmail Trigger').item.json.Subject }}\nBody:{{ $('Gmail Trigger').item.json.snippet }}\nSnippet:{{ $('Gmail Trigger').item.json.snippet }}",
        "options": {},
        "requestOptions": {}
      },
